metadata.description:
"...The Viperous and Deceit, Angelica..."

She's one of my OCs of VILLIAN. If I were you I won't let her touch me. Angelica is a scientist and researcher in criminal association that ruled by Monica.

She likes to invent and modify many experimental humans in many ways that don't want to know what she did to them... Many assistants she has in her lab was her invention too.
